 age of 18 or 19. Her story has captured the imagination of many writers, and she is variously portrayed as a national and political hero, a model of apolitical straightforwardness and honesty, and a religious heroine. She was canonized in  1920 . More recent influences have included the American film actress  Joan Crawford  (  1908–77 , born  Lucille le Sueur ), the British actress  Joan Collins  (  b. 1933 ), the American comedienne  Joan Rivers  (  b. 1933 ), and the West Indian pop singer  Joan Armatrading  (  b. 1950 )."],"variants":[{"name":"John","meanings":["Greek: the Lord gave graciously; whom Jehovah gave; whom Jehovah bestowed."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Joan had at least 1 son with sir, John II Loudham ,of Frense. She died after 1329."},"et":{"–after 1329":"–pärast 1329","–1329":"–1329","by 1329":"1329","after 1329":"pärast 1329","1329 ?":"1329","1329":"1329"},"fi":{"–after 1329":"–1329 jälkeen","–1329":"–1329","by 1329":"1329","after 1329":"1329 jälkeen","1329 ?":"1329","1329":"1329"},"fr":{"–after 1329":"–après 1329","–1329":"–1329","by 1329":"1329","after 1329":"après 1329","1329 ?":"1329","1329":"1329","lifeSummary":"Joan a eu au moins 1 fils avec sir, John II Loudham ,of Frense. Elle est décédée après 1329."},"de":{"–after 1329":"–nach 1329","–1329":"–1329","by 1329":"1329","after 1329":"nach 1329","1329 ?":"1329","1329":"1329","lifeSummary":"Joan hatte mit sir, John II Loudham ,of Frense mindestens 1 Sohn. Sie starb nach 1329."},"ht":{"–after 1329":"–after 1329","–1329":"–1329","by 1329":"1329","after 1329":"after 1329","1329 ?":"1329","1329":"1329"},"hu":{"–after 1329":"–1329 után","–1329":"–1329","by 1329":"1329","after 1329":"1329 után","1329 ?":"1329","1329":"1329"},"id":{"–after 1329":"–setelah 1329","–1329":"–1329","by 1329":"1329","after 1329":"setelah 1329","1329 ?":"1329","1329":"1329"},"it":{"–after 1329":"–dopo il 1329","–1329":"–1329","by 1329":"1329","after 1329":"dopo il 1329","1329 ?":"1329","1329":"1329","lifeSummary":"Joan lei avuto alm